## .profile

I usually place binaries like micro, amfora, youtube-dl in ~./local/bin (labeled as General below)

```
# Go
export PATH=$PATH:~/.local/go/bin:~/go/bin
export GOPATH=$HOME/go

# General
export PATH=$PATH:~/.local/bin
```
